### PDF Ingestion Test Cases

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1/agent

### Test 1: Ingest PDF with default parameters
# This will upload a PDF file with default chunk size and overlap
# The source will be the filename without extension
POST {{baseUrl}}/ingest/pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pdfFile"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Test 2: Ingest PDF with custom source name
# This will upload a PDF and use a custom source identifier in the knowledge base
POST {{baseUrl}}/ingest/pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pdfFile"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source"

my-knowledge-document
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Test 3: Ingest PDF with custom chunk parameters
# This will upload a PDF with custom chunk size and overlap
POST {{baseUrl}}/ingest/pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pdfFile"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source"

my-document
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="chunkSize"

750
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="chunkOverlap"

100
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Test 4: Search the knowledge base
# After ingesting PDFs, you can search for content
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "search term from your PDF"
}

### Test 5: Chat with RAG (using ingested PDF)
# The agent will use RAG to find relevant content from ingested PDFs
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Ask a question about the content in your ingested PDF"
}

### Test 6: Ingest plain text (existing endpoint for reference)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This is some test content that will be chunked and stored in the knowledge base.",
  "source": "test-document",
  "chunkSize": 500,
  "chunkOverlap": 50
}
